# Learning Path Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create learning path (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/learning-paths
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Backend Mastery",
  "track": "BACKEND",
  "description": "Learn backend skills"
}

### Get learning path by track (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/learning-paths/track/BACKEND

### Get all learning paths (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/learning-paths

### Get learning path by ID (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/learning-paths/{{id}}

### Update learning path (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/learning-paths/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "description": "Updated details"
}

### Delete learning path (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/learning-paths/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
